= Personal Interests

This page documents all my interests that do not fit into research or professional interests.

I am a voracious reader, and I especially like reading comic books, fantasy novels and science fiction. I also indulge in recreational mathematics, programming, crosswords, board games, movies and television and have a layman's interest in history and mythology.

== Clubs

